title: Gold Mid main lf duo/possibly clash team
body:
Hey guys,

I've been having really bad luck trying to get out of gold so I'm looking for someone reliable/mature to duo with. Preferably a jungler but I really don't care as long as you know how to win. Please look me up as Eitarin; shoot me an invite if you're down. I'll be on shortly after posting this.

I might also be looking for a clash team because I'm not sure if mine's going to go ahead again cause the guy leading it is pretty done with league due to the same problem I'm having I believe. Anyway yeah let me know. 

Cheers.
